summary: Thumper  Pt 1 Pt 2 Ever since the encounter, Thumper (nicknamed by his brothers due to his loud heart beat) has been sick to his...
caption:
Thumper 

Pt 1 Pt 2

Ever since the encounter, Thumper (nicknamed by his brothers due to his loud heart beat) has been sick to his stomach. He tells all of his brothers his problem and questions what has happened but they all give him the same answer with little explanation: He has a crush! 

OC’s in order of appearance:

Hops, Medic

Gunner, heavy trooper

Taya Natali, (new) Jedi Knight, general

Captain Jace, Captain

I want to draw these bbys more in the future! If you have OC’s you’d like to share please tell me about them!!!

((IDK why the quality drops in the last three frames??))

blog.name: stateofdisunion
blog.title: State of DisUnion
blog.description:
Learn about United States History from the States themselves as they try to get along despite their many, many difference!
- Updates Tuesday at 6PM CST

Mini Blog 3/5/2019: I will be appearing at the Woman of Wonder Con! this Saturday (March 9th). It is a FREE event at the Dallas Public Library, so if local, come check it out!

- For Sketches and Asks follow The DisUnion Ask/Sketch Blog @Disunionsketches

Note: This Webcomic was developed independently from and is not related to Hetalia. It is in fact how I learned about Hetalia. However, I appreciate all the support and love the fandom has shown for my states!

summary: Featured Avatar: Arizona For this week, feel free to ask questions about little Ari here (or heck anyone!) over on the askblog  ...
caption:
Featured Avatar: Arizona

For this week, feel free to ask questions about little Ari here (or heck anyone!) over on the askblog   (no really please ask questions. I would love to answer questions!) ETA: TUMBLR WON’T LET THE ASKBLOG ACCRPT QUESTIONS. YAY. so until I get this sorted out, just ask here and I can answer and reblog to the ask blog.

Arizona the youngest of the continental states, also one of the loudest and rashes, and as you can see, a metal-head. 

Warning on this one. 
Arizona is a state whose personality I built around a lot of negative impacts the American minority representation/treatment has had/can have
He is nowhere near as secure in or as proud of his Hispanic identity as Nevada, New Mexico, or Florida and there is a lot of self-hatred below. 

Arizona was first noticed around the beginning of the 1800′s by New Mexico and remained toddler sized for most of the next decade, only really beginning to grow in the early 1900′s.

He’s never been very sure of his cultural identity having grown up with many of the Anglo-states putting down his Hispanic heritage and making him fail as though he were inferior to them because of her heritage (and that he needed to learn their ways-so the “White Man’s burden” philosophy). New Mexico did her best to combat this, but she was often unable to see him and/or had many of her own struggles. 

Despite this, New Mexico did try to keep Arizona close as she did not want another Texas. This, unfortunately, had the opposite effect up to and including Arizona siding with Texas during the Civil War just to annoy new Mexico (not that it meant much. he was really to young to understand what was going on). 

Arizona does love his Big Sister though, though they have lots of arguments and he is closer to Texas who he considers the “fun” sibling. He still identifies and appears as a Hispanic state though, so this gives New Mexico hope. 

The dysphoria he feels about his own identity - as well as the way he and New Mexico were treated by other states-fuels a lot of rage in him. He often lashes out at his own heritage, but also at anything else around him. His temper is very short and he often feels he needs to fight to prove himself. 

California introduced him to Heavy Metal as an outlet for his anger and he has taken to it hugely (seriously there is a huge metal scene in that state!) and it has helped a bit. He as even begun to write Metal songs in Spanish, much t New Mexico’s delight. 

Because of his temper though, he isn’t very close to most state’s. He prefer the company of his pet Scorpion “Scorpy,” or Texas if he wants to talk. New Mexico if he wants to sit quietly and feel safe. 

Aside from Heavy Metal, he enjoys architecture and is actually quite good at designing homes. He also enjoys quietly sitting alone in his dessert and taking in how pretty it is. 

Often if he can’t be found, he is off camping by himself trying to figure out how he feels about a lot of things.

blog.name: surferofrowdybliss
blog.title: Visual Play
blog.description:
Deborah Coulter

Scissors in hand, I make collages exploring the freedom and fun of visual play. I get lost in the joy of selecting, cutting, and rearranging images. The process begins as I discover the infinite possibilities life offers through the spaciousness of an open heart. Children, animals, and nature lead the way.

I invite you to join me in these adventures of scissors & glue blending with imagination in the exquisite present.

https://instagram.com/deborahcoulterartflow/

http://society6.com/deborahcoulter

blog.title: Wʜᴇʀᴇ I ᴀᴛᴛᴇᴍᴘᴛ ᴛᴏ ᴀʀᴛ.
blog.description:
Wᴇʟᴘ ʜᴇʀᴇ's ᴡʜᴇʀᴇ I ᴍᴏᴠᴇᴅ ᴛᴏ ᴋɪᴅᴅᴏs, ᴀɴᴅ I ᴘʟᴀɴ ᴛᴏ ʙᴇ ᴍᴏʀᴇ ᴀᴄᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴀɴᴅ sᴇʀɪᴏᴜs ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴍʏ ᴀʀᴛ ᴛʜɪs ᴛɪᴍᴇ ᴀʀᴏᴜɴᴅ.
I'ᴍ sᴏʀʀʏ ꜰᴏʀ ᴀɴʏᴏɴᴇ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ʜᴀᴅ ᴛᴏ ᴅᴇᴀʟ ᴡɪᴛʜ ᴍʏ ɪɴᴀᴄᴛɪᴠɪᴛʏ ᴏɴ ᴍʏ ᴏʟᴅ ᴀᴄᴄᴏᴜɴᴛ. Fᴏʀ ᴛʜᴏsᴇ ᴛʜᴀᴛ ᴀʀᴇ sᴛɪʟʟ ᴀʀᴏᴜɴᴅ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ᴛʜᴇ Uɴᴅᴇʀᴛᴀʟᴇ ʙʟᴏɢ, I ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇ ʏᴏᴜ ᴛᴏ ᴛʜᴇ ᴍᴏᴏɴ ᴀɴᴅ ʙᴀᴄᴋ.💛💛💛
